category.name: sci-fi/fantasy
description:
Welcome to Stockholm Anime Society.

This meetup group is a gathering place for anime and manga enthusiasts. Meet new friends and talk about your favorite Anime/Manga, games, films, TV series etc. Or share your own art and fiction! Whatever interests you have are welcome here.

We will aim to meet once per week and watch anime, or maybe go for a friendly fika. Information about each event will be posted within the event info. It is of course free to join!

We hope that this will lead to favorable social interactions and maybe more sophisticated appreciation of Japanese animation.

P.S. We have a private Facebook group, please feel free to join it!

category.name: sci-fi/fantasy
description:
Calling all otaku and cosplayers in Malmö!

This is a meetup to connect with fellow anime and cosplay fans and to share our passion and joy over our favorite fictional characters, shows and movies! Experience old and new shows and movies together. Compare dakimakuras and duel it out over who has the best waifu/husbando!

We will hold our meetups at Spelens Hus in Malmö, where there is a large viewing area with a projector and lots of seats. As well as video game consoles, board games and even an area with sewing machines where the cosplayers can craft their own outfits! And much more!

Feel free to join our MyAnimeList club and share your favorite anime/manga! MAL Club

So join us and experience the world of anime and cosplay with your fellow otaku, today!

category.name: sci-fi/fantasy
description:
Welcome to Stockholm Anime Society.

This meetup group is a gathering place for anime and manga enthusiasts. Meet new friends and talk about your favorite Anime/Manga, games, films, TV series etc. Or share your own art and fiction! Whatever interests you have are welcome here.

We will aim to meet once per week and watch anime, or maybe go for a friendly fika. Information about each event will be posted within the event info. It is of course free to join!

We hope that this will lead to favorable social interactions and maybe more sophisticated appreciation of Japanese animation.

P.S. We have a private Facebook group, please feel free to join it!

category.name: sci-fi/fantasy
description:
Calling all otaku and cosplayers in Malmö!

This is a meetup to connect with fellow anime and cosplay fans and to share our passion and joy over our favorite fictional characters, shows and movies! Experience old and new shows and movies together. Compare dakimakuras and duel it out over who has the best waifu/husbando!

We will hold our meetups at Spelens Hus in Malmö, where there is a large viewing area with a projector and lots of seats. As well as video game consoles, board games and even an area with sewing machines where the cosplayers can craft their own outfits! And much more!

Feel free to join our MyAnimeList club and share your favorite anime/manga! MAL Club

So join us and experience the world of anime and cosplay with your fellow otaku, today!
name: Malmö Anime & Cosplay Nation
